<h2>Detailed Description</h2><div>This class provides a character set conversion system. You instanciate it by passing the FROM and TO charsets, and it can do stateful conversions. (ie, convert multiple buffers one after the other, while taking care of characters split between two buffers.<br /></div><div style="margin-top:3em;border:1px solid #aaa;border-bottom-style:none;border-left-style:none;border-right-style:none"></div>
